  "texts": [
    "If PAI were connected to the internet and tried to disempower humanity, this would likely make it impossible to simply 'turn it off', since it could distribute copies of itself over the internet.",
    "Moreover, for reasons of efficiency, there are calls to give AI access to military equipment.",
    "To summarize, both control over important pieces of infrastructure as well as the possibility of AI's improving themselves support the view that even many kinds of PAIs are capable of disempowering humanity.",
    "The more powerful AI is, the worse humanity's chances are of resisting attempted disempowerment.",
    "Finally, when talking about superintelligence, it is hard to conceive of scenarios where the superintelligence would not be able to disempower humanity."
  ],
